  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >***At the moment the only 100% compatible resolution is 16:9***</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of Balls is a not-so-new game from our brand-not-so-new team based on a... not so brand new concept, BUT with a lot of brand new twists!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the Paddle as you destroy countless blocks & ships while Boosting, Shooting and Shielding at your own will!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 7 Gamemodes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 30 Levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Custom Level Editor: Pick between pre-existing layouts, events and gamemodes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Asymmetrical Local Multiplayer Bonus Mode: Play with a friend assisting you or screwing you over...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 Extras: A space shooter, a space clicker and a quiz!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >***At the moment the only 100% compatible resolution is 16:9***</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of Balls is a not-so-new game from our brand-not-so-new team based on a... not so brand new concept, BUT with a lot of brand new twists!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the Paddle as you destroy countless blocks & ships while Boosting, Shooting and Shielding at your own will!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 7 Gamemodes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 30 Levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Custom Level Editor: Pick between pre-existing layouts, events and gamemodes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Asymmetrical Local Multiplayer Bonus Mode: Play with a friend assisting you or screwing you over...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 Extras: A space shooter, a space clicker and a quiz!</p></li></ul>",
